Champion Select

Pick

     
       "The guilty will know agony."

Ban

     
       "I am forsaken."

Original Original Arclight Arclight Cosmic Hunter Cosmic Hunter PROJECT PROJECT

Each of these skins feature some additional quotes and interactions, but otherwise use the Classic voiceover. Some Classic voicelines may also be disabled while using alternate skins.

Heartseeker Varus uses the same voicelines as Arclight Varus.
