Trivia

     
       "I do what I must." is similar to  
      Lee Sin OriginalCircle.png "We do what we must."
     
       "Beware a man with nothing to lose." is based on an Italian proverb "Beware of one who has nothing to lose".
     
       "No turning back." is similar to  
      Ezreal PulsefireCircle.png "No turning back now." and  
      Irelia OriginalCircle old2.png "There's no turning back."


